---
// CTA final — mur noir avec Calendly
---

<section id="contact" class="py-20 md:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
    <div
      class="bg-ink text-paper rounded-sketch-b border-2 border-ink p-8 md:p-20 relative overflow-hidden"
      data-reveal
    >
      <!-- Meta -->
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[#FC5D10] mb-8">
        // Last section
      </p>

      <!-- Headline XXL -->
      <h2 class="font-display text-[56px] md:text-[120px] leading-[0.9] mb-8">
        On en parle <span class="text-[#FC5D10]">30 min</span> ?
      </h2>

      <!-- Sous-titre -->
      <p class="font-body text-lg md:text-2xl text-paper/80 mb-12 max-w-2xl leading-snug">
        Call découverte. Gratuit. Direct. Sans bullshit.<br />
        On regarde ton besoin, je te dis si je peux aider.
      </p>

      <!-- CTAs -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-6 mb-12">
        <a
          href="https://calendly.com/maxgarandel-pro/30min"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="cta-pill inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-orange text-white border-2 border-paper rounded-sketch-a px-8 py-4 font-mono text-base font-semibold"
          data-cursor="hover"
        >
          📅 Réserver un call →
        </a>

        <a
          href="mailto:maxgarandel.pro@gmail.com"
          class="font-note text-2xl md:text-3xl text-paper hover:text-orange transition-colors underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4"
          data-cursor="hover"
        >
          maxgarandel.pro@gmail.com
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Info bar -->
      <div class="border-t-2 border-paper/20 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-paper/60">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#FC5D10] animate-pulse"></span>
          Réponse sous 24h ouvrées
        </div>
        <div>Basé à Rennes · Remote</div>
        <div>Freelance — SIRET dispo</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Accent décoratif -->
      <div
        class="absolute top-8 right-8 md:top-16 md:right-16 w-32 h-32 md:w-48 md:h-48 rounded-full bg-[#FC5D10] opacity-20 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
      ></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
